<li>Did you hear about the turkey that cursed a lot? It had a fowl mouth.</li>
<li>I can‚Äôt eat any more Thanksgiving leftovers. I‚Äôm quitting cold turkey!</li>
<li>I gave him some pie to apologize. It was a piece offering. <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/16.0.1/72x72/262e.png" alt="‚òÆ" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></li>
<li>Did you hear about the fighting bakers? They didn‚Äôt see pie to pie.</li>
<li>What did the Pilgrims use to make cakes? May flour.</li>
