										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It‚Äôs almost autumn, the most wonder-fall time of the year! And we‚Äôve got a cornucopia of fall puns ready to harvest for all your seasonal marketing, social media, email, and copywriting needs.</p>
<p>We‚Äôve got fall fashion puns, sappy tree puns, fun food puns, and hilarious holiday puns. We even asked a few popular AI tools to spin up some of their best fall puns. So put your messaging on autumn-matic and use these acorn-y puns before autumn leaves.</p>
<h3>Contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#best-fall-puns">Best fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#cute-fall-puns">Cute fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#fall-puns-for-marketing">Fall puns for marketing</a></li>
<li><a href="#funny-fall-puns">Funny fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#fall-tree-puns">Fall tree puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#fashionable-fall-puns">Fashionable fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#food-related-fall-puns">Food-related fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#halloween-and-thanksgiving-fall-puns">Halloween and Thansgiving fall puns</a></li>
<li><a href="#fall-puns-from-ai-tools">Fall puns from AI tools</a></li>
</ul>
<div id="best-fall-puns"></div>
<h2>Best fall puns</h2>
<p>Let‚Äôs get rolling with some totally autumn puns you can drop into just about any <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/fall-marketing-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fall messages and marketing</a>.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fall-puns-wordstream-pumpkin.webp" alt="Fall puns - Instagram post with a pumpkin pun" width="386" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-93654 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fall-puns-wordstream-pumpkin.webp 386w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/fall-puns-wordstream-pumpkin-193x300.webp 193w" sizes="(max-width: 386px) 100vw, 386px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/B2rYaAYnqah/?igsh=MWUxMWZ0dXo3a2F1Mg%3D%3D" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Source</em></a></p>
<ul>
<li>Falls well that ends well.</li>
